This test shows the number of cases that offload succeeds depending on the
average/constant packages size.


TEST E (OK)

This test shows the energy saving vs the extra time needed to offload.

- r = sum(RES_A(:,2))
- eje = transpose([1:r])
- plotyy(eje,RES_D(:,1),eje,RES_D(:,2),'bar','stem')